  "resolutionRules": [
    "Blueprint capability slots and module provides/requires use only executable mechanic refs pinned to mechanicId, revision, and contentHash.",
    "Discovery mechanic entries cannot participate in online composition until promoted into approvedRevisions.",
    "Bare mechanic labels are invalid machine input.",
    "A mechanic entry cannot redefine semantic meaning or GDJS instruction signatures.",
    "New mechanics are added by immutable revision and cross-reference closure checks, never by Planner switch branches."
